title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 186-1.2 - Scope
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 186-1.2 - Scope

State Regulations

This regulation shall apply to all child performers who
either reside or work in New York State and to the entities employing
them. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12

186-1.2
